Padre-Plugin-Shell-Base
=======================

A base class for plugins that use the system shell to extend Padre.

INSTALLATION
============

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION
=========================

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Padre::Plugin::Shell::Base

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Padre-Plugin-Shell-Base

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Padre-Plugin-Shell-Base

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Padre-Plugin-Shell-Base

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Padre-Plugin-Shell-Base/


